title.narrative: 4.2 Increased access of Lebanese and Non-Lebanese youth (15-24 years) to technical and vocational training and innovative skills building programmes for improved professional readiness and employability.

description.narrative: UNICEF increased the employability of 32,508 (42 % Male; 58% Female) youth through access to BLN, TVET, skills training and innovation courses, and increased its support to youth to transition from learning to earning through employment support services, business incubation, Cash for Work programmes and other income generating activities. | Status:Constrained | As-of Date:17/01/2020
